# Repo-only tooling/docs for extensions must not ship in the root
# @diegopetrucci/pi-extensions package tarball (each extension's own
# workspace package.json "files" allowlist already excludes these, but
# npm does not honor a workspace's package.json "files" field when the
# workspace directory is packed as part of the ROOT package's "extensions"
# directory entry -- see test/publish-safety.test.mjs for the regression
# check). Add new repo-only extension subdirectories here as needed.
dynamic-context-pruning/scripts/
dynamic-context-pruning/docs/
